title: ICPC Azerbaijan Regional Contest 2025
organization: ICPC Foundation / Azerbaijan Higher Education Institutions
description: Achieved a standout performance at the ICPC Azerbaijan Regional (Republican) Championship, competing against the nation's elite university teams. Earned a 'Third Award' for exceptional algorithmic problem-solving and efficiency in a high-stakes competitive environment. Recognized with an 'Honorable Mention' for technical excellence. The contest required solving complex challenges involving advanced data structures, dynamic programming, and sophisticated graph algorithms under intense time pressure.
